reviewText: Klatts DVDs are all the same. very little medical info given

this DVD has a lot of info about knife wounds after viewing this DVD you wull know that a person using a knife is bad news hopefully help you if stab or cut up by crazy person with a knife great first aid DVD

Excellent training dvd on treating knife wounds. The main instructor in the dvd is a subject matter expert on emergency tactical first aid and guides you through the process of effectively dealing with knife wounds.  Great training tool!
